                    expenditures in either <gloss target="#t_FY1">FY</gloss> 1954 or <gloss
                        target="#t_FY1">FY</gloss> 1955 for the following programs: Spain, <gloss
                        target="#t_PICMME1">PICMME</gloss>, <gloss target="#t_UNKRA1">UNKRA</gloss>,
                    escapees, materials development, and <gloss target="#t_DOT1">DOT</gloss>’s; and
