                    expenditures in either <gloss target="#t_FY1">FY</gloss> 1954 or <gloss
                        target="#t_FY1">FY</gloss> 1955 for materials development or the <gloss
                        target="#t_DOT1">DOT</gloss>’s; and that the expenditures allowed will be
